Why does expected utility matter?Published on December 25, 2023 2:47 PM GMT<br/><br/><p>在不确定性下决策的背景下，我们考虑最大化预期货币收入和预期效用的策略；我们提供一个论点来表明，在某些假设下，最大化预期货币收入是合理的，然后我们证明该论点不适用于预期效用。我们剩下的问题是如何证明预期效用最大化策略的合理性。</p><h2><strong>预期货币收入</strong></h2><p><br>假设你要从预期经济回报分别为 1$ 和 2$ 的两个游戏 A 和 B 中选择一个，这两个游戏具有一定的概率分布。 </p><figure class="image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ALtFyrzvrNZPbfKBJ/orpsrqmn22lmqnunkegw" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ALtFyrzvrNZPbfKBJ/aqmsg1a464xb5cydadzs 160w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ALtFyrzvrNZPbfKBJ/m2jxmaxr1hu280wkvmvc 320w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ALtFyrzvrNZPbfKBJ/ynigdcofrkmmpbuwgjyx 480w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ALtFyrzvrNZPbfKBJ/sgsadwgm2an1obfktliv 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ALtFyrzvrNZPbfKBJ/gstdcsykdsglfbrs1wj1 800w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ALtFyrzvrNZPbfKBJ/oj9u0uqazt8senl21raq 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ALtFyrzvrNZPbfKBJ/luuuuyktlmobxgehp7kv 1120w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ALtFyrzvrNZPbfKBJ/yctg0hsnp8hsd2khlai3 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ALtFyrzvrNZPbfKBJ/py5lendpv8ygk7vcidof 1440w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ALtFyrzvrNZPbfKBJ/stsvudjfborad6rrwdh3 1517w"></figure><p>如果你玩很多次，比如说 N，大数定律和中心极限定理可能会变得相关，并且 A 和 B 重复的概率分布将使其质量分别在 N 和 2N 附近越来越明显地分开。 <br></p><figure class="image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ALtFyrzvrNZPbfKBJ/gospdhhvwls5n6ahtysf" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ALtFyrzvrNZPbfKBJ/rqswyc5ykoxodzz6e1bz 150w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ALtFyrzvrNZPbfKBJ/ibpxygylmj0l3i9ldqww 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ALtFyrzvrNZPbfKBJ/arinq6h1ymczrwuqwl4t 450w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ALtFyrzvrNZPbfKBJ/n9lvkvnppvpdrauxdv6k 600w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ALtFyrzvrNZPbfKBJ/yedqan0m3vbbetrck17i 750w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ALtFyrzvrNZPbfKBJ/zojpcxiglivf90kfd3s4 900w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ALtFyrzvrNZPbfKBJ/w1etm9csu5fsoah4q9rf 1050w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ALtFyrzvrNZPbfKBJ/zxjrmeongo2fkncm0b3p 1200w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ALtFyrzvrNZPbfKBJ/sj1jgjrcpw3x4p1zdlde 1350w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ALtFyrzvrNZPbfKBJ/osrriojjbkpte9zzdqpc 1490w"></figure><figure class="image"><img></figure><p>至此，很明显，你多次玩 B 比多次玩 A 更好。您可以通过计算 A 和 B 的预期收益来提前预测这一点。因此，假设您可以在 A 和 B 之间做出“很多”选择，您一定会选择预期利润较高的一个。但如果你只能做出一个选择怎么办？如果 A 和 B 的分布重叠，预期利润还重要吗？</p><p>即使您只需做出一次特定选择，它也可能是一长串许多不同选择中的一个，并不总是在 A 和 B 之间，而是在其他选项集之间。即使选择不同，我们仍然可以设法利用 LLN 和中心极限定理。假设我们在两个游戏之间有大量选择：</p><ul><li>时间0：在游戏<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A_0"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">0</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>之间选择<style>.mjx-chtml {display: inline-block; line-height: 0; text-indent: 0; text-align: left; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 100%; font-size-adjust: none; letter-spacing: normal; word-wrap: normal; word-spacing: normal; white-space: nowrap; float: none; direction: ltr; max-width: none; max-height: none; min-width: 0; min-height: 0; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 1px 0}
