</style>和<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="B_0"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">0</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li><li>时间 1：在<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A_1"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>和<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="B_1"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>之间选择</li><li>时间2：...</li><li> ...</li><li>时间 N：在<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A_N"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.085em;">N</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>和<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="B_N"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.085em;">N</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>之间选择</li></ul><p>我们再次希望，如果你总是选择预期回报较高的游戏，随着时间的推移，对于大 N 来说，统计随机性将变得越来越无关紧要，并且与采用不同策略的人相比，你将存储更多的钱。</p><p>为了让这个希望真正实现，我们需要游戏<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A_k"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.219em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">k</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>和<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="B_k"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.219em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">k</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>的收入统一有界，并且与 N 相比“足够小”。如果例如：</p><ul><li>单场比赛就像<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/St._Petersburg_paradox">圣彼得堡的比赛</a>一样有无限的期待；</li><li>一款游戏的预期收入如此之大，使得之前的所有结果几乎变得无关紧要；</li><li>该系列游戏的预期收入不断增长。</li></ul><p>如果所有游戏的收入都位于“有限”值范围内，而 N 与该范围相比“足够大”，则确实可能发生这种情况。</p><p>实现这一目标的要素包括：</p><ul><li>我们从游戏中获得的金钱的可加性属性（重要的是我们可以存储金钱并且金额永远不会重置）；</li><li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Central_limit_theorem#Lindeberg_CLT">非同分布变量的中心极限定理</a>。</li></ul><p>总结一下：如果你可以存储或花掉所有的钱，并且该选择是一组许多选择的一部分，并且与其他选择相比，其均值和标准差较小，那么始终选择使预期货币收入最大化的选项的策略确实是合理的。预计总共存储的资金总额。</p><h2><strong>预期效用</strong></h2><p>向我们的财富添加新资金的效果可能会有所不同，具体取决于我们目前已有的财富（10,000 美元对于没有钱的人比百万富翁更有意义）。我们通过定义一个“效用”函数来模拟这一事实，该函数代表额外的钱对特定人的生活的影响。我们可以预期这个效用函数<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="U(x)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.084em;">U</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>随着货币数量<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="x"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>的增加而增加（越多越好），并且其斜率总是减小（我们越富有，我们就越不关心多 1 美元），如下所示： </p><figure class="image image_resized" style="width:63.11%"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ALtFyrzvrNZPbfKBJ/xvlj0yyatj7ul31ku0fd" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ALtFyrzvrNZPbfKBJ/cubfertajlabmlug7fmi 150w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ALtFyrzvrNZPbfKBJ/yij3czgmhns6kyfdsuow 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ALtFyrzvrNZPbfKBJ/uzjlpzngye3qlykwink8 450w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ALtFyrzvrNZPbfKBJ/mgkdhbng01gqxefjvd3k 600w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ALtFyrzvrNZPbfKBJ/v5fhkiktfcdl3plfmrxl 750w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ALtFyrzvrNZPbfKBJ/miehwq5aex11hbpozwm2 900w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ALtFyrzvrNZPbfKBJ/m6zba0uepbn3joolzp3s 1050w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ALtFyrzvrNZPbfKBJ/cmrpfony9oqrf7nrwz53 1200w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ALtFyrzvrNZPbfKBJ/wqabns3kyll4hgfzqsal 1350w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ALtFyrzvrNZPbfKBJ/ermioboleks9h6fpsfqs 1422w"></figure><p>如果可以的话，理性的代理人不会被期望最大化他的货币收益，而是最大化他的“效用”收益。但当他必须在不确定的情况下对这个新目标做出选择时，会发生什么呢？</p><p>假设我们必须选择玩游戏 A 或游戏 B，收入有一定的概率分布。与我们在上一段中所说的关于货币收入的内容类比，我们可能会想说，我们不是选择具有最大预期货币收入的游戏，而是选择具有最大预期<i>效用的游戏。</i></p><p>示例：如果游戏 A 可以让我们以 0.5 的概率赢得 1 美元，或者什么都没有，而游戏 B 可以让我们以 0.3 的概率赢得 2 美元，或者什么也没有，我们对预期的娱乐不再感兴趣，即：</p><p> <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="E(A)=0.5 \times 1=0.5"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.026em;">E</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">0.5</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">×</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">0.5</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> ， <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="E(B)=0.3\times 2=0.6"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.026em;">E</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">0.3</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">×</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">0.6</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p><p>我们不选择 B 因为<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="0.6>0.5"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">0.6</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">>;</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">0.5</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> ，我们计算预期的效用</p><p><span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="E(U(A))=0.5\times 